9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"After a global war, the seaside kingdom known as the Valley of the Wind remains one of the last strongholds on Earth untouched by a poisonous jungle and the powerful insects that guard it. Led by the courageous Princess Nausicaä, the people of the Valley engage in an epic struggle to restore the bond between humanity and Earth."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/101984/nausica-of-the-valley-of-the-wind"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"After a global war, the seaside kingdom known as the Valley of the Wind remains one of the last strongholds on Earth untouched by a poisonous jungle and the powerful insects that guard it. Led by the courageous Princess Nausicaä, the people of the Valley engage in an epic struggle to restore the bond between humanity and Earth."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/101984/nausica-of-the-valley-of-the-wind"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tcrkfB8SRPQCgwI88hQScua6nxh.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"After a global war, the seaside kingdom known as the Valley of the Wind remains one of the last strongholds on Earth untouched by a poisonous jungle and the powerful insects that guard it. Led by the c